criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age>18 years;

          -  Patients with CKD stage 3-5, patients on dialysis or KTx patients with confirmed
             COVID-19, at minimum 2 weeks after the confirmed test;

          -  Age, sex and kidney disease (CKD stage 3-5, dialysis or KTx) matched patients without
             confirmed SARS-CoV-2 infection.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prior diagnosis of pulmonary fibrosis, pneumectomy or massive pleural effusion;

          -  Active malignancies.

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Active systemic infections (due to difficulties in the interpretation of nonspecific
             inflammation biomarkers in this type of patients);

          -  Congenital heart disease.
